FileHistory.send_file(request)[source]¶

Send a file through Django without loading the whole file into memory at once. The FileWrapper will turn the file object into an iterator for chunks of 8KB.

FileHistory.send_zipfile(request)[source]¶

Create a ZIP file on disk and transmit it in chunks of 8KB, without loading the whole file into memory. A similar approach can be used for large dynamic PDF files.
